| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2307 — Recovery Inhibition (cactus)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3f0a5f9e-6b4c-5846-b365-1d72cad4d368"
